==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: comeuppance
<hw>come`up"pance</hw> <pr>(k⟦ucr⟧m`⟦ucr⟧p"p⟦ait⟧ns)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<def>An unpleasant experience a person endures, which is viewed by
others as a just retribution for bad behavior; just deserts; <as>as, the
Senator took bribes for years, and finally got his <ex>comeuppance</ex>
when he was caught in a sting operation</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

